     <div id="lead" class="article-perex ">
          <p>The coronavirus isn't the only plague making headlines this year -- locusts are devastating crops in several parts of the world, and now scientists are discovering why the pest forms destructive swarms.</p>
     </div>

                            
                                
                            
                                












    <div class="article-gallery " >
            <div  class="image-container" id="article-main-image">
                
                <picture data-image-source="article_photo" data-caption="Record numbers of locusts have descended in devastating swarms across parts of Africa and Asia this year" class="image-wrapper"><source data-original="//ocdn.eu/pulscms-transforms/1/xRXk9kuTURBXy83YjgxMWIwZC00ZTMyLTQ5MjEtYmIyOC05MzhiNDRlZDA3YTAuanBlZ5GTBc0DFs0BroGhMAU" srcset="//ocdn.eu/pulscms-transforms/1/xRXk9kuTURBXy83YjgxMWIwZC00ZTMyLTQ5MjEtYmIyOC05MzhiNDRlZDA3YTAuanBlZ5GTBc0DFs0BroGhMAU" type="image/webp"><img width="790" height="430" alt="Record numbers of locusts have descended in devastating swarms across parts of Africa and Asia this year" title="Record numbers of locusts have descended in devastating swarms across parts of Africa and Asia this year" src="//ocdn.eu/pulscms-transforms/1/HyKktkuTURBXy83YjgxMWIwZC00ZTMyLTQ5MjEtYmIyOC05MzhiNDRlZDA3YTAuanBlZ5GTBc0DFs0Brg" data-original="//ocdn.eu/pulscms-transforms/1/HyKktkuTURBXy83YjgxMWIwZC00ZTMyLTQ5MjEtYmIyOC05MzhiNDRlZDA3YTAuanBlZ5GTBc0DFs0Brg" class="image "></picture> <link rel="preload" as="image" href="//ocdn.eu/pulscms-transforms/1/xRXk9kuTURBXy83YjgxMWIwZC00ZTMyLTQ5MjEtYmIyOC05MzhiNDRlZDA3YTAuanBlZ5GTBc0DFs0BroGhMAU">
            </div>

        
            <div class="imgMetaData">
                
                    <span class="caption">Record numbers of locusts have descended in devastating swarms across parts of Africa and Asia this year</span>
                

                
                

                

                

                <div class="clear"></div>
            </div>
        
